node.text:
Hippos have the ability to lock their jaws at nearly 180 degree angles 😍 This feature, which makes a hippo look like it’s yawning, is particularly important when hippos end up in conflict with other animals. The wide opening angle means that hippos can produce a bite force of 1,800 PSI—enough to break bones and snap wooden planks in two.

📽️ @cincinnatizoo #hippos #animals #science #interesting

node.text:
Postcards from Turkey 🏞🍃 Have you ever been to this beautiful country before?

Turkey has 44 National Parks that look after its stunning natural heritage – so if you decide to visit, you’ll have plenty of options to choose from (some of our favorites are the Yedigoller National Park and the Saklikent Milli Park). 🌳🇹🇷

📷 @cumacevikphoto #travel #turkey #globe
📍Turkey
